reviewText: What can anybody say about Brooks and Dunn?  They are pretty fabulous talents, and none of these videos disappoint.Too bad they broke up, but I guess everything has to eventually come to an end, especially teams.  After all, Martin & Lewis did, and didn't Abbott & Costello?I only wish they had had "Believe" on here.  That was pretty great, but it wasn't part of the deal.

reviewText: Unlike the last 2 reviewers, I will NOT say Don't buy. I say, if you like Brooks and Dunn, enjoy watching music videos, and have a DVD player, buy it. Because, as we all know, vhs tapes deteriorate in time, but DVDs don't. It may be the same as the vhs but I gaurantee you that it will be alot better when you watch it on DVD cause of the higher quality sound and video.
summary: Awesome video collection from Country music's top duo
